{"id":258924,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-上海维权者沈金宝等人在北京声援失踪多/","date":"2012-10-24T14:16:19Z","modified":"2012-10-24T14:16:19Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权者沈金宝等人在北京声援失踪多日的朱金娣（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，上海市的上访维权人士沈金宝从上海躲避截访者的层层阻扰到达北京，声援已经失踪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>天的朱金娣。沈金宝与另一位上海的上访维权人士李雪美一起，为声援朱金娣被失踪第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>天而到国家信访局、全国人大、中纪委，反映、投诉、举报，控告上海地方政府随意限制公民人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日下午，朱金娣在北京最高法院正常上访时，遭到上海地方政府派遣的保安人员绑架。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时</span><span>许，朱金娣被押回上海，被关押在沪东街道政府私自设立在浦东大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2900</span><span>号金华旅馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span><span>房间的黑监狱内，派</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6~7</span><span>个保安</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时把守门口，不让她出房门一步。沪东街道政法委书记王纪兵、信访综治科的韩俊当时到黑监狱不是为朱金娣解决上访问题，而是恐吓朱金娣说：“访民无论到北京或北戴河都是违法的”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣因担心家中患忧郁症的儿子，她拨打了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">168</span><span>个“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>”报警电话求助，无一出警。朱金娣逼迫无奈之下自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日起</span><span>进行绝食裸体抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>朱金娣与朋友通话时，有人猛烈敲房门，并且大声呼喊“快开门、快开门”。此时，朱金娣与朋友的通话中断，从此失去联系，至今已经第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣家的房屋遭到强拆，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年分配得到浦东新区东波路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">585</span><span>弄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span><span>室的动迁安置房屋，居住</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>年的安置房的产权证却被法院判给与该套房屋无关的人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>，朱金娣儿子的门面商铺，位于上海市浦东大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">651</span><span>弄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">102</span><span>室被政府打着世博动迁通道的旗号强拆（土地且荒芜至今）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>由此引发朱金娣上访维权，因上访长期被监控、多次被关黑监狱、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次刑事拘留等迫害，她儿子忧郁症的病情越来越严重，无生活来源，无人问津，急需朱金娣的照料。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>各地上访维权者得知朱金娣的遭遇后，不由感慨：和谐社会，财产被抢。阳光政策，无家可归。依法维权，被关黑牢。以人为本，还我人权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-At6w4LsUd3Q/UIeu0I2jnDI/AAAAAAAAR4Q/ntkF3z2vS2A/s1600/564.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-At6w4LsUd3Q/UIeu0I2jnDI/AAAAAAAAR4Q/ntkF3z2vS2A/s320/564.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OWBhEYmTznM/UIeu7MhUnfI/AAAAAAAAR4Y/cNETPUwDdLE/s1600/569.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"251\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OWBhEYmTznM/UIeu7MhUnfI/AAAAAAAAR4Y/cNETPUwDdLE/s320/569.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hOHpYNy9_2I/UIevEkXlbnI/AAAAAAAAR4g/2TIbeJ9VFQ8/s1600/%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8E%E6%B2%88%E9%87%91%E5%AE%9D%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B1%E8%B8%AA%E7%AC%AC55%E5%A4%A9.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hOHpYNy9_2I/UIevEkXlbnI/AAAAAAAAR4g/2TIbeJ9VFQ8/s320/%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8E%E6%B2%88%E9%87%91%E5%AE%9D%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B1%E8%B8%AA%E7%AC%AC55%E5%A4%A9.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>李雪美与沈金宝抗议朱金娣被失踪第55天</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0MED3FcpTEg/UIevMODhm4I/AAAAAAAAR4o/L5eUozEo1uI/s1600/%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-0MED3FcpTEg/UIevMODhm4I/AAAAAAAAR4o/L5eUozEo1uI/s320/%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4464262385262563207?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}